===========================
Radiant
===========================
The micro-framework based on Silex, with support for AWS-SDK.
That help you develope small responsive websites and APIs for yours mobile apps.

====================
Goals for this project:
====================
1. Create APIs supported by mobile apps, hosted on AWS.
2. Create small websites with the best SEM and SEO.
3. More ...

=====================
Install
=====================
#> php composer.phar install

=====================
Radiant example
=====================

Open http://localhost/app/web/index.php

=====================
